---
title: Welcome
description: Watch as Troy Vassalotti learns his way around a computer.
layout: primary
pageCSS: homepage
animation: true
pageName: homepage
---
<main class="grid place-center">
  <section class="animated-header">
    <h1 class="typewriter typewriter__1">Hey, I'm Troy...</h1>
    <p class="typewriter typewriter__2">...and I make things.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="section contain" id="posts">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
      <p>Everyone's got a blog these days, am I right? Keep up with my latest projects and what's happening in the very particular piece of my life I decide to share with you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="posts">
      <div class="grid full-width post-listing__container">
      {%- for post in collections.post.slice(collections.post.length - 2, collections.post.length) | reverse -%}
        <article class="post-listing">
          <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        </article>
      {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>
    {% button '/posts/', 'Read my posts', 'My Posts', '' %}
  </section>
  <section class="section contain" id="projects">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Projects</h2>
      <p>These are some of my favorite projects, but I have many more.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="collection center-txt">
      {% for project in projects.homepage -%}
        <figure>
          <a href="{{ project.href }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <img src="/assets/img/{{ project.img }}.jpeg" alt="{{ project.alt }}" width="320" height="180" loading="lazy"/>
          </a>
          <figcaption>{{ project.caption }}</figcaption>
        </figure>
      {% endfor -%}
    </div>
    {% button '/projects/', 'View my projects.', 'My Projects', '' %}
  </section>
  <section class="section contain" id="music">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Music</h2>
      <p>When Iâ€™m not coding, maybe I'm writing.</p>
      <p>My friends and I started Front Royal with the desire to make a name for ourselves, and I started troy. to explore a new outlet.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="collection music">
      <div id="frontRoyal">
        {% linkedPicture 'https://frontroyalmd.bandcamp.com/', 'front-royal-logo-white_400x240', 'The logo for my band, Front Royal.', 'png', 400, 240 %}
      </div>
      <div id="troy">
        {% linkedPicture 'https://justtroy.bandcamp.com/', 'troy-full', 'The logo for my band, troy.', 'png', 600, 300 %}
      </div>
    </div>
    {% button '/music/', 'Learn more about my music.', 'My Music', '' %}
  </section>
  <section class="section contain" id="contact">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Reach Me</h2>
      <p>Take a look around and if you like what you see then feel free to get in touch.</p>
    </div>
    {% contactForm %}
  </section>
</main>
